     1                     period2, lnYc, sigmac,iflag )
            attenname1 = 'Syn. Rupture: Youngs+AS (M7.4)-Rock'
c     Youngs et al (1997) Horizontal, subduction, Rock
c     with Idriss (1991:1995) Horizontal Crustal
C     Model Number = 7201043
